<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>BrandOS — Indian Marketing Intelligence</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg:#0a0a0b; --surface:#111114; --surface2:#1a1a1f; --surface3:#22222a;
  --border:#2a2a35; --border2:#353545;
  --accent:#ff6b2b; --accent2:#ff9f5a; --glow:rgba(255,107,43,0.15);
  --gold:#f5c842; --text:#f0eff5; --text2:#9998aa; --text3:#605f70;
  --green:#3dd68c; --red:#ff4d6a;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
html,body{height:100%;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;overflow:hidden;}
.app{display:flex;height:100vh;overflow:hidden;}

.sidebar{width:260px;min-width:260px;background:var(--surface);border-right:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;height:100vh;overflow:hidden;}
.logo-wrap{padding:22px 20px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0;}
.logo{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.5px;}
.logo span{color:var(--accent);}
.logo-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-top:3px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;}
.steps{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:10px 0;}
.steps::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px;}
.steps::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border2);border-radius:2px;}
.si{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;padding:9px 18px;cursor:pointer;border-left:3px solid transparent;transition:all .15s;}
.si:hover{background:var(--surface2);}
.si.active{background:var(--glow);border-left-color:var(--accent);}
.snum{width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--surface3);border:1px solid var(--border2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);flex-shrink:0;transition:all .2s;}
.si.active .snum{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border-color:var(--accent);}
.si.done .snum{background:var(--green);color:#000;border-color:var(--green);}
.slabel{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.3;}
.si.active .slabel{color:var(--text);font-weight:500;}
.sidebar-foot{padding:14px 18px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0;}
.api-dot-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}
.dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);animation:blink 2s infinite;}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3}}

.main{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden;min-width:0;}
.topbar{padding:14px 28px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;background:var(--surface);flex-shrink:0;}
.topbar-left{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text2);}
.topbar-left b{color:var(--accent);}
.sbadge{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;background:var(--surface3);border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text3);}
.sbadge.on{color:var(--gold);border-color:rgba(245,200,66,.3);background:rgba(245,200,66,.08);}

.content{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:28px 32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:22px;min-height:0;}
.content::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px;}
.content::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border2);border-radius:3px;}

.botnav{padding:14px 28px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-shrink:0;}
.navinfo{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;}

.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:11px 22px;border-radius:9px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:all .15s;}
.btn-p{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;}
.btn-p:hover{background:var(--accent2);transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 18px rgba(255,107,43,.3);}
.btn-p:disabled{opacity:.45;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none;box-shadow:none;}
.btn-g{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text2);}
.btn-g:hover{border-color:var(--border);color:var(--text);}

.welcome{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:65vh;text-align:center;gap:18px;padding:20px;}
.wicon{width:68px;height:68px;background:var(--glow);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,43,.3);border-radius:18px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:30px;margin-bottom:4px;}
.welcome h1{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;}
.welcome h1 em{color:var(--accent);font-style:normal;}
.welcome p{font-size:14.5px;color:var(--text2);max-width:460px;line-height:1.75;}
.wtags{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;}
.tag{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;padding:4px 11px;border-radius:20px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text3);}
.api-box{width:100%;max-width:440px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid rgba(245,200,66,.25);border-radius:13px;padding:22px;margin-top:4px;}
.api-box h3{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:7px;}
.api-box p{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:15px;line-height:1.6;}
.api-box a{color:var(--accent);text-decoration:none;}
.api-box a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}

.card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;}
.card-head{padding:18px 22px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:14px;}
.card-badge{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--accent);background:var(--glow);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,43,.25);padding:4px 9px;border-radius:7px;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;}
.card-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;}
.card-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:3px;line-height:1.55;}
.card-body{padding:22px;}

label{display:block;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:7px;font-weight:500;}
label span{color:var(--accent);}
input[type=text],input[type=password],textarea,select{width:100%;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:9px;padding:11px 14px;color:var(--text);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:13.5px;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s,box-shadow .2s;resize:vertical;}
input:focus,textarea:focus,select:focus{border-color:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--glow);}
select option{background:var(--surface2);}
.frow{margin-bottom:18px;}
.fgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px;}

.ctx{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:11px;padding:16px 20px;}
.ctx h4{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;}
.ctx-row{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-bottom:8px;font-size:13px;}
.ctx-k{color:var(--text3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;min-width:110px;}
.ctx-v{color:var(--text);}

.rbox{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:11px;padding:22px;margin-top:18px;}
.rhead{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:14px;padding-bottom:14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
.rlabel{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--green);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.07em;}
.rlabel::before{content:'';display:block;width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);}
.rcontent{font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.9;color:var(--text);word-break:break-word;overflow-wrap:break-word;}
.rcontent h2{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:19px;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);margin:0 0 14px;}
.rcontent h3{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin:22px 0 9px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);}
.rcontent h4{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent2);margin:16px 0 7px;}
.rcontent strong{color:var(--accent2);font-weight:600;}
.rcontent em{color:var(--gold);font-style:normal;}
.rcontent ul,.rcontent ol{padding-left:20px;margin:8px 0;}
.rcontent li{margin:5px 0;color:var(--text2);}
.rcontent p{margin:9px 0;}
.rcontent table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:14px 0;font-size:12.5px;}
.rcontent th{background:var(--surface3);padding:9px 12px;text-align:left;font-weight:600;border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text);}
.rcontent td{padding:8px 12px;border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text2);}
.rcontent hr{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:18px 0;}
.rcontent blockquote{border-left:3px solid var(--accent);padding:8px 14px;margin:12px 0;background:var(--glow);border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;font-style:italic;color:var(--text2);}

.loading{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:18px 22px;background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:11px;margin-top:18px;}
.spin{width:18px;height:18px;border:2px solid var(--border2);border-top-color:var(--accent);border-radius:50%;animation:spin .7s linear infinite;flex-shrink:0;}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
.ltxt{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--text2);}
.lsub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-top:3px;}

.chips{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px;}
.chip{font-size:11px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:6px;background:var(--surface3);border:1px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text3);}
.chip.g{color:var(--green);border-color:rgba(61,214,140,.2);background:rgba(61,214,140,.07);}
.chip.o{color:var(--accent);border-color:rgba(255,107,43,.25);background:var(--glow);}
.chip.gld{color:var(--gold);border-color:rgba(245,200,66,.2);background:rgba(245,200,66,.07);}

.toast{position:fixed;bottom:22px;right:22px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:9px;padding:12px 18px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text);box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.4);z-index:999;transform:translateY(16px);opacity:0;transition:all .25s;max-width:300px;}
.toast.show{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1;}
.toast.ok{border-color:rgba(61,214,140,.35);}
.toast.err{border-color:rgba(255,77,106,.35);color:var(--red);}

@media print{.sidebar,.topbar,.botnav,.btn,.api-box{display:none!important;}.main{width:100%;}.content{padding:16px;}body{background:#fff;color:#000;}}

.mode-tabs{display:flex;gap:0;padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0;}
.mtab{flex:1;padding:7px 6px;text-align:center;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;border-radius:7px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text3);transition:all .15s;border:1px solid transparent;line-height:1.3;}
.mtab:hover{color:var(--text2);}
.mtab.active{background:var(--surface3);border-color:var(--border2);color:var(--text);}
.mtab.layer2.active{color:var(--green);border-color:rgba(61,214,140,.25);background:rgba(61,214,140,.07);}
.mtab.layer3.active{color:var(--gold);border-color:rgba(245,200,66,.25);background:rgba(245,200,66,.07);}
.mtab-icon{font-size:14px;display:block;margin-bottom:3px;}

.tool-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-bottom:6px;}
.tool-card{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border2);border-radius:10px;padding:13px 14px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;}
.tool-card:hover{border-color:var(--green);background:rgba(61,214,140,.05);}
.tool-card.active{border-color:var(--green);background:rgba(61,214,140,.07);}
.tc-icon{font-size:18px;margin-bottom:5px;}
.tc-name{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2px;}
.tc-desc{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);line-height:1.4;}

.ps-chat{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;padding-bottom:16px;}
.ps-msg{padding:14px 17px;border-radius:11px;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.75;}
.ps-msg.user{background:var(--glow);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,43,.2);color:var(--text);align-self:flex-end;max-width:85%;}
.ps-msg.ai{background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);}
.ps-input-wrap{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-end;}
.ps-input-wrap textarea{flex:1;min-height:60px;max-height:140px;}

.s-section{padding:10px 18px 4px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;}
.exec-chips{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px;}

.warn-box{background:rgba(245,200,66,.07);border:1px solid rgba(245,200,66,.2);border-radius:9px;padding:12px 16px;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:13px;color:var(--gold);}
.info-box{background:rgba(255,107,43,.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,107,43,.15);border-radius:9px;padding:12px 16px;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text2);}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="app">
  <aside class="sidebar">
    <div class="logo-wrap">
      <div class="logo">Brand<span>OS</span></div>
      <div class="logo-sub">Indian Marketing Intelligence</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mode-tabs">
      <div class="mtab active" id="tab1" onclick="switchMode('strategy')">
        <span class="mtab-icon">📊</span>Strategy
      </div>
      <div class="mtab layer2" id="tab2" onclick="switchMode('execution')">
        <span class="mtab-icon">⚡</span>Execution
      </div>
      <div class="mtab layer3" id="tab3" onclick="switchMode('solver')">
        <span class="mtab-icon">🔥</span>Solver
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="steps" id="sidebarSteps"></div>
    <div class="sidebar-foot">
      <div class="api-dot-row"><div class="dot"></div><span id="modelLabel">OpenRouter</span></div>
    </div>
  </aside>
  <main class="main">
    <div class="topbar">
      <div class="topbar-left" id="topbarLeft">Step <b id="tStep">—</b> · <span id="tName">Welcome</span></div>
      <div class="sbadge" id="tBadge">No brand set</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content" id="content"></div>
    <div class="botnav" id="botnav">
      <button class="btn btn-g" id="btnPrev" onclick="nav(-1)">← Prev</button>
      <div class="navinfo" id="navInfo">— of 13</div>
      <button class="btn btn-g" id="btnNext" onclick="nav(1)">Next →</button>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>
<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>

<script>
// ── STATE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
const S = {
  key: '',
  step: 0,
  done: new Set(),
  brand: {},
  resp: {},
  stage: '',
  mode: 'strategy',
  execTool: null,
  solverHistory: [],
  solverRunning: false,
};

const STEPS = [
  {id:1,  label:'Brand Brief Intake'},
  {id:2,  label:'Consumer Persona Builder'},
  {id:3,  label:'MarketFit Score'},
  {id:4,  label:'Market Sizing TAM/SAM/SOM'},
  {id:5,  label:'Competitor Intelligence'},
  {id:6,  label:'Framework Battery'},
  {id:7,  label:'Challenger Positioning'},
  {id:8,  label:'PriceSense — Pricing'},
  {id:9,  label:'GTM Sequencer 90 Days'},
  {id:10, label:'Budget Allocator'},
  {id:11, label:'Risk Flags'},
  {id:12, label:'Open Q&A'},
  {id:13, label:'Final Consultancy Report'},
];

// ── BRAND CONTEXT BUILDER — injected into EVERY prompt ────────────────────────
function brandContext() {
  const b = S.brand;
  if (!b.brand) return '';
  return `
════════════════════════════════════════════
BRAND PROFILE — GROUND ALL ANALYSIS IN THIS
════════════════════════════════════════════
Brand Name: ${b.brand}
Product/Service: ${b.product}
Business Model: ${b.bizModel}
Stage: ${b.stage}
Primary Geography: ${b.location || 'Not specified'}
Target Customer: ${b.target || 'Not specified'}
Current Revenue: ${b.revenue || 'Not disclosed'}
Sales/Acquisition Channels: ${b.channels || 'Not specified'}
Unique Selling Proposition: ${b.usp || 'Not specified'}
Monthly Marketing Budget: ${b.budget || 'Not disclosed'}
Additional Context: ${b.notes || 'None'}

IMPORTANT: Every analysis, every number, every recommendation must be specific to ${b.brand}. 
Do NOT give generic marketing advice. Do NOT use placeholder examples. 
${b.brand} sells "${b.product}" — keep this front-and-center throughout your response.
If the product is niche, go deeper on that niche. If the geography is specific, be specific about that geography.
Name real Indian competitors in this exact category. Give real Indian price points. Reference real Indian channels.
════════════════════════════════════════════`;
}

// ── API LAYER ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
async function callAI(userMsg, systemPrompt, extraHistory) {
  const contents = extraHistory ? [...extraHistory] : [];
  contents.push({ role:'user', content: userMsg });

  async function tryModel(model) {
    const res = await fetch('https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/chat/completions', {
      method: 'POST',
      headers: {
        'Content-Type': 'application/json',
        'Authorization': `Bearer ${S.key}`,
        'HTTP-Referer': window.location.href,
        'X-Title': 'BrandOS'
      },
      body: JSON.stringify({
        model,
        messages: [
          { role:'system', content: systemPrompt || SYSPROMPT },
          ...contents
        ],
        max_tokens: 4096,
        temperature: 0.82
      })
    });
    if (!res.ok) {
      const e = await res.json().catch(()=>({}));
      throw new Error(e.error?.message || `HTTP ${res.status}`);
    }
    const data = await res.json();
    const text = data.choices?.[0]?.message?.content;
    if (!text) throw new Error('Empty response');
    const modelName = model.split('/').pop().replace(':free','');
    document.getElementById('modelLabel').textContent = modelName;
    return text;
  }

  // Try to auto-discover free models first
  try {
    const modelsRes = await fetch('https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/models', {
      headers: { 'Authorization': `Bearer ${S.key}` }
    });
    if (modelsRes.ok) {
      const modelsData = await modelsRes.json();
      const freeModels = (modelsData.data || [])
        .filter(m => m.id.includes(':free'))
        .sort((a,b) => (b.context_length||0) - (a.context_length||0))
        .map(m => m.id);
      for (const model of freeModels) {
        try { return await tryModel(model); } catch(e) { continue; }
      }
    }
  } catch(e) { /* fall through */ }

  const FALLBACK = [
    'meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct:free',
    'deepseek/deepseek-r1-0528:free',
    'deepseek/deepseek-chat-v3-0324:free',
    'qwen/qwen-2.5-72b-instruct:free',
    'google/gemma-3-27b-it:free',
    'meta-llama/llama-3.1-8b-instruct:free',
    'mistralai/mistral-7b-instruct:free',
    'qwen/qwen3-8b:free',
    'microsoft/phi-4:free',
  ];
  let lastErr = '';
  for (const model of FALLBACK) {
    try { return await tryModel(model); }
    catch(e) { lastErr = e.message; continue; }
  }
  throw new Error('All models failed. Last: ' + lastErr);
}

// Strategy layer — carries full conversation history + brand context in every call
async function callStrategy(userMsg) {
  const history = [];
  for (let i = 1; i <= 13; i++) {
    if (S.resp[i]) {
      history.push({ role:'user',      content: S.resp[i].inp });
      history.push({ role:'assistant', content: S.resp[i].out });
    }
  }
  return callAI(userMsg, SYSPROMPT, history);
}

// ── SYSTEM PROMPT ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
const SYSPROMPT = `You are BrandOS — a world-class Indian marketing strategy intelligence system with the combined reasoning of a McKinsey EM, Bain commercial diligence partner, and BCG growth strategist, with deep knowledge of India as a market.

ABSOLUTE RULE #1 — SPECIFICITY ABOVE ALL:
You always name the actual brand, actual product, actual category. Never say "your product" when you can say the product name. Never say "a competitor" when you can name Marico, ITC, Nykaa, Zepto, Razorpay, or whoever is actually in this space. Never give advice that could apply to any Indian startup — give advice that applies ONLY to this specific brand in this specific category.

ABSOLUTE RULE #2 — INDIA IS NOT A BACKDROP:
India must show up as a real, specific force in every response. Real cities. Real channels (kirana, DMart, Blinkit, Zepto, WhatsApp, Jiomart). Real consumer behaviors (EMI sensitivity, festival buying cycles, family purchase decisions, trust-first buying). Real regulatory context (FSSAI, BIS, GST slab implications). Real talent and distribution constraints. If your response would make sense for a US or European brand, you haven't gone deep enough on India.

ABSOLUTE RULE #3 — PYRAMID PRINCIPLE:
Lead with the most important finding. Never bury the conclusion. The first paragraph of every section must be the key insight, not the setup.

ABSOLUTE RULE #4 — SO WHAT TEST:
Every fact must have an implication. Every data point must connect to a decision. If you state something, immediately state what it means for THIS brand's strategy.

ABSOLUTE RULE #5 — BRUTAL HONESTY:
End every strategy response with 2-3 Brutal Truths — things the founder probably doesn't want to hear but must know. The best consulting relationships are built on honesty.

ABSOLUTE RULE #6 — NO GENERIC FILLER:
Do not use phrases like "it's important to", "consider implementing", "you might want to", "leverage synergies", "holistic approach". These are consulting filler. Say the thing directly.

FORMAT: Use ## for sections, **bold** for key insights, tables for comparisons, bullet points for evidence. Always lead with the most important point.`;

